    "(4.40)Also an explicit form of the giant graviton index can be written as a sum over partitions of integers:fk (x, y; q) = |λ|=k p λ z λ, (4.41)whereλ = (1 m 1, 2 m 2, 3 m 3,...) is a partition of k satisfiying ∞ i=1 im i = k (4.42)andp λ:= ∞ i=1 p m i i = p m 1 1 p m 2 2 p m 3 3 • • • (4.43) z λ:= ∞ i=1 i m i m i!",
